## Quick reference

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Local Docker dev | `docker compose up --build` |
| Docker production | `docker compose -f docker-compose.prod.yml up -d` |
| Docker CI / tests | `docker compose -f docker-compose.test.yml up --abort-on-container-exit` |
| PaaS setup | `my deploy setup --provider <provider>` |
| Terraform (AWS/GCP/Azure) | `my deploy terraform --provider <provider>` |
| Deploy / push | `my deploy push --provider <%= provider %>` |
| Status | `my deploy status --provider <%= provider %>` |
| Logs | `my deploy logs --provider <%= provider %>` |
| Secrets sync | `my deploy secrets sync --provider <%= provider %>` |
| Rollback | `my deploy rollback --provider <%= provider %>` |
| Destroy | `my deploy destroy --provider <%= provider %>` |

